Comment: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartA————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:38.88,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.14,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙要讓人等到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:44.38,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,到底幹什麼才能那麼花時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.74,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:49.59,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,從那傢伙出去已經過去多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:50.86,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,三天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:52.69,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:54.82,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙到底有多蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:59.60,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,再說那傢伙應該也是被村民排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:03.54,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞如果再出了什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:04.55,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,別生氣別生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:09.17,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽要穿的…婚紗來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:13.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是找那個花了很多時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:15.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:17.34,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是這樣也沒辦法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:20.93,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算是這樣也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:25.48,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,他的壽命也沒有長到可以這樣揮霍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:33.32,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  爸爸不是說會一起來  永遠在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.96,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽不幸福嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.20,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,當然幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.78,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再稍微等一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:49.98,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  時間靜止的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:53.03,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡會是什麼感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.86,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣？媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:57.50,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:09.23,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,這種地方竟然有房子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:13.24,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的距離為什麼到現在都沒人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:16.22,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(930,990)}TSUKIHIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:16.22,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是擄走少年兵的怪物的腹地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:22.47,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是少年兵那傢伙說怪物是自己的妻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:25.31,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物是少年兵的妻子？怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:29.91,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是怪物用妖術操縱了少年兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:34.52,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,想要通過操縱少年兵  有朝一日襲擊村子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.98,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果變成那樣只能夠處理掉少年兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.26,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你們聽好  趁早幹完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.81,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.57,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你磨蹭個什麼  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:52.26,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:55.10,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼…剛才好像有腳步聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.95,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.31,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.75,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(813,990)}SHION
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.75,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:08.69,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉了嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.39,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  果斷一發解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.85,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽  媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.78,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這是怪物的女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.63,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}媽媽…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:19.54,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那頭髮  肯定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.66,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  把這傢伙也幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.31,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂  她還很小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:26.92,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,磨磨蹭蹭的搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.91,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  讓我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.59,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目隱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.20,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？！消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.53,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…妖術？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:38.68,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.19,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.42,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目欺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.14,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目奪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:00.43,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.56,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,東躲西藏也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:13.76,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,縱使逃至天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:16.18,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,爾等所在之處也立可知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:18.77,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:19.82,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:25.36,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不願直言則讀透汝心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.55,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目竊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:33.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快說怪物在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:38.36,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不然…我們也不想打你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:42.15,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…也不能放任來歷不明的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(741,990)}AZAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,薊…薊是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.05,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不准…出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.54,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  為什麼要包庇那個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.20,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人類吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:58.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,還要反抗的話…不會輕饒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.09,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不是包庇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.60,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不是全部說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:07.95,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和她…和家人永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:09.42,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:14.69,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！似乎發現信號一類的東西了  一直延續到森林那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:15.99,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:20.55,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是少年兵為回去而準備的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.92,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,立即為退治怪物做準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:26.40,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多給我清醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:29.33,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,把她解決掉後  你也會清醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.18,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快點做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.67,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.87,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,滾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.03,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:44.10,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,然後永遠不許帶任何人來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.68,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了就趕快給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.12,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:08.89,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.48,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,別再靠近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:18.45,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再因我而讓你們受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.59,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.27,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.65,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,想要逃避世間之理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.82,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,並且還把你們也牽連進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.76,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,其實已經意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.75,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有我在就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:41.50,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只要沒有我  你們就能在這個世界上幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.87,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我沒有期盼幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:48.79,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只是稍微做了一會兒夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.51,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,能永遠和家人生活在一起的幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.17,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,太美好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.68,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真是無可救藥得美好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.69,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:04.21,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  你不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.61,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要使用這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:09.86,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我沒有這樣說的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:14.91,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要作為一個人類  和父親一起幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.30,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的…幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:20.99,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！媽媽別走！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:26.35,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  對不起  對不起  對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.55,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠愛你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:34.54,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我會永遠祈禱你們能幸福  永遠…
Comment: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartB————————
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉這樣不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想要擅自出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  別說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你讀連環畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到這裡一起讀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就讀這個故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天開始  從媽媽留下我們消失那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底過了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸去世的時候  茉莉呱呱墜地的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽都沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽現在也在那個沒有終結的世界一個人生活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一人等待著不知會不會歸來的媽媽也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等茉莉再大些  就讓她見見外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界肯定會接受她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像媽媽對我所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在對我來說茉莉的幸福就是我的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  不知道什麼時候睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:10:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！在就應答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？喂  怪物不是說只有一隻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別老想著以前的傳說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也靠它找到了有意思的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  這頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候做成展示品的話肯定能大賺一筆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼  住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個  放開那孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？區區個怪物說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實點！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  要把他也一起抓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你在聽我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  媽媽  我們…沒有變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到  連她們也拉進這邊了  您真是壞心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個永不結束的世界的痛苦您不是最清楚的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  不會閉嘴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順從於利己又輕鬆的欲望  創造出這個世界的不正是大人您嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來您的願望是把最愛的家人一起帶到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是很好嘛  女兒和孫女一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願望終於實現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  真是愚蠢  沒錯  沒錯  就要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是我們的最大的快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  這都是我的錯  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  就是這個表情  太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  對  就是這樣  變成這種悲劇全都是因為您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少  至少只有這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己丟掉了女王蛇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那個附身的話  確實能救那孩子一命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這樣也就沒有抑制這個世界的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附身於您的蛇失去了女王是多麼的混亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請放心吧  至少不會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您對這世界所下達的把8月15日逝去的生命捲進來這條命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是無法停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  要是不離家出走就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且都是修哉不好  都是修哉欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不聽使喚地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  你和家人走散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我也和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色的眼睛也是一個樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  不要再走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰…來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是…女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是一個人  好寂寞  一個人好寂寞啊  誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來  不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我眼睛的話就會變成石頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…我必須得是一個人  所以請回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼喚我的人就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  我和你是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都被別人忌諱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全用不著害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…那個…做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我睡著了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  他去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都太過份了  把我丟下一起走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有人在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎  會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口…口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  請喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不燙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  嗯  不燙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  你是從哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在那裡睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  記性不怎麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記性不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也經常忘記東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然覺得要是能都記得就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一個  我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼  是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要朋友  想和朋友一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋…友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  但是我只記得這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和朋友一起玩耍  只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以介紹我的朋友給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…大家一定很樂意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經深夜0時了  還有如此人群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信  到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如您所見  非常的吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:20:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上是從現場發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也去吧  大家一定都在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的朋友
Comment: 0,0:22:40.93,0:22:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartC————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女失去了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的重要的朋友  全都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女一個人哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再一次和大家一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女無數次如此祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼向少女搭話了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現您的願望吧  實現您的渴望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為您帶來一個能實現您的空想的世界吧
